around here, sailor.

00:24.591 --> 00:26.359
That's Denny Crane?

00:26.392 --> 00:27.160
The Denny Crane?

00:27.193 --> 00:28.128
BILLINGS: Don't be fooled.

00:28.161 --> 00:29.229
Once he's in the courtroom,

00:29.262 --> 00:30.697
