00:33.667 --> 00:36.069
It's not enough
to insist on fidelity

00:36.402 --> 00:37.203
or fair dealing.

00:37.237 --> 00:39.706
A good leader
has to practice it.

00:39.740 --> 00:41.174
FOREPERSON:
"Was the defendant's termination

00:41.207 --> 00:42.308
of the plaintiff wrongful?",

00:42.342 --> 00:43.476
we find in the affirmative.

00:43.510 --> 00:44.811
We order the defendant to pay

00:44.845 --> 00:47.213
the plaintiff $2.3 million.

00:47.247 --> 00:49.616
SHORE: Denny,
this is Tara Wilson.

00:49.650 --> 00:52.352
