or nothing.

02:18.417 --> 02:20.587
But my point,

02:20.621 --> 02:21.988
nobody could have known

02:22.022 --> 02:23.389
about this drug deal, Jimmy.

02:23.423 --> 02:25.458
I didn't tell no one.

02:25.491 --> 02:27.528
I think the FBI bugged me.

02:27.561 --> 02:28.595
I'm positive.

02:28.629 --> 02:31.297
Bugged you? How?

02:31.331 --> 02:33.767
They inserted some device
in my buttocks.

02:34.701 --> 02:36.670
I know it sounds nuts,

02:36.703 --> 02:38.271
but I think during
the first surgery,

02:38.304 --> 02:40.406
