02:43.910 --> 02:45.912
It's the only way they could
have known about the pot.

02:45.946 --> 02:46.947
I mean, I didn't talk
about this deal

02:46.980 --> 02:48.281
on the phone or nothing,

02:48.314 --> 02:50.483
