what you plan to say?

04:18.418 --> 04:19.485
No idea.

04:19.920 --> 04:22.322
ROSE: Most paralegals
request not to work with me.

04:22.355 --> 04:24.057
Just so you know,
I am totally fine

04:24.090 --> 04:26.092
