06:31.998 --> 06:32.699
YOUNG: Desperate?

06:32.733 --> 06:34.134
Oh, it feels desperate?

06:34.167 --> 06:35.702
BERLUTI:
Eugene, if the evidence

06:35.736 --> 06:36.870
doesn't get suppressed,

06:36.903 --> 06:38.739
