double-spaced.

07:01.167 --> 07:02.468
That's far
too complicated to--

07:02.503 --> 07:03.970
One page, double-space,

07:04.004 --> 07:04.638
off you go.

07:04.671 --> 07:05.806
Denny...

07:05.839 --> 07:07.473
CRANE: Edmond,
are we on today?

07:07.508 --> 07:09.776
EDMOND: Uh, no.
I have an emergency.

07:09.810 --> 07:11.512
