07:34.501 --> 07:36.436
He's a wonderful
young man, Denny,

07:36.469 --> 07:37.370
and you know him.

07:37.403 --> 07:39.372
He would--

07:39.405 --> 07:42.042
Edmund...

07:42.075 --> 07:43.777
I'll take care of it.

07:48.081 --> 07:50.016
