the only one

08:28.795 --> 08:30.296
who can handle
this man, Matthew.

08:30.330 --> 08:32.065
You need to somehow
rein him in--

08:32.097 --> 08:33.833
This is Alan Shore,
Sheldon.

08:33.866 --> 08:35.736
In addition to being
a gifted attorney,

08:35.769 --> 08:36.937
he's an accomplished

08:36.970 --> 08:38.104
Denny Crane wrangler.

08:38.138 --> 08:39.706
He'll join you
at tomorrow's trial.

08:39.740 --> 08:40.741
