I'll make it up to you.

09:30.196 --> 09:31.532
Pretty please?

09:32.633 --> 09:33.333
Hmm?

09:34.801 --> 09:36.570
Date rape.

09:36.603 --> 09:38.238
Mmm.

09:38.271 --> 09:40.841
