09:46.146 --> 09:48.181
FRUTT: Not that client.

09:48.214 --> 09:50.617
FRUTT: Manny is one
of my oldest friends.

09:50.651 --> 09:51.484
YOUNG: Jimmy,

09:51.518 --> 09:52.753
