who you're talking to?

17:02.302 --> 17:04.871
Look...

17:04.905 --> 17:06.940
I offer this because,

17:06.973 --> 17:09.041
"A," I don't care
if I get fired,

17:09.075 --> 17:12.278
and, "B," someone
very dear to me

17:12.311 --> 17:14.180
died with Alzheimer's.

17:14.981 --> 17:18.318
And when I think
I see symptoms,

17:18.351 --> 17:22.623
even the possibility
of symptoms...

17:28.261 --> 17:29.996
The fact that you may have
Alzheimer's

17:30.030 --> 17:32.498
does not entitle you
to criticize me.

17:35.001 --> 17:35.936
Denny...

17:37.370 --> 17:40.240
these people, the Finnertys,

17:40.273 --> 17:43.644
have waited 14 months for trial.

17:43.677 --> 17:45.411
You--
They want me.

17:45.445 --> 17:47.914
SHORE: Because they think
you're prepared.

17:47.948 --> 17:51.752
Who do you think you are, hmm?

17:51.785 --> 17:52.886
I hire you,

17:52.919 --> 17:54.087
you're here a week,

17:54.120 --> 17:56.056
now you're trying
to tell me what to do?

17:56.089 --> 17:57.891
Nobody, nobody...

17:59.726 --> 18:02.703
tells me what to do.

18:09.976 --> 18:10.744
Dad...

18:13.446 --> 18:14.347
you're my father,

18:14.380 --> 18:16.316
