19:02.402 --> 19:03.804
and it still does.

19:05.405 --> 19:06.873
Really?

19:06.907 --> 19:09.075
BERLUTI: Get some space
in the North End,

19:09.109 --> 19:10.343
wake up every morning,

19:10.376 --> 19:11.277
drop my laundry off

19:11.311 --> 19:12.646
at the Fluff and Fold,

19:12.679 --> 19:14.047
have coffee
with Lenny and Sal

19:14.080 --> 19:15.682
