she's got no credit,

19:22.756 --> 19:24.057
negotiate a better price

19:24.090 --> 19:27.761
on a condo for my Aunt Mary,

19:27.794 --> 19:30.296
help the people
I really care about

19:30.330 --> 19:32.933
to live better lives,
you know.

19:32.966 --> 19:34.568
Then close up early enough

19:34.601 --> 19:37.638
to have supper with them.

19:37.671 --> 19:40.874
That sounds like a life to me,

19:40.907 --> 19:42.442
a rich one, even.

19:49.449 --> 19:50.517
You have to do it.

19:51.785 --> 19:52.753
Do what?

19:52.786 --> 19:54.821
Hang a shingle
on the North End,

19:54.855 --> 19:55.956
help Aunt Mary
