20:04.270 --> 20:05.338
of all times.

20:05.371 --> 20:07.040
STRINGER: Jimmy,
the word on the street

20:07.073 --> 20:10.476
is our firm is over.

20:12.846 --> 20:14.615
I've been looking.

20:16.116 --> 20:17.183
